\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 The\'a0
\f2\i main
\f1\i0 \'a0focus of the assignment is to do the inheritance correctly! Place any members as high in the heirarchy as possible, but only as high as makes sense. The Noble battle method should only be defined once, not once for each possible combination of Nobles. Make use of abstract methods / classes where appropriate.\
